#: .\melee.json
msgid "Flower Pot"
msgid_plural "Flower Pots"
msgstr[0] "花盆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Flower Pot', 'str_pl': 'Flower Pots'}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"This is a flower pot made of clay. It is big enough for most of crops along "
"with plants. Growth time of plants ranges from approximately 16 days to "
"approximately 121 days. When plants have fully grown, a pot with them like "
"this should be activated, then crafted into an empty pot. This provides with"
" edible or usable, or both, plants."
msgstr ""
"這是一個由粘土製成的花盆。它足夠大，可以容納大多數作物和植物。植物的生長時間大約從16天到121天不等。當植物完全長成時，應激活這樣一個裝有植物的花盆，然後將其製作成空盆。這會提供可食用或可用，或兩者兼有的植物。"

